quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,48,"They had already sought to spread discord before and devised every ˹possible˺ plot against you ˹O Prophet˺, until the truth came and God’s Will prevailed—much to their dismay"
  9,49,"There are some of them who say, “Exempt me and do not expose me to temptation.” They have already fallen into temptation. And Hell will surely engulf the disbelievers"
  9,50,"If a blessing befalls you ˹O Prophet˺, they grieve, but if a disaster befalls you, they say, “We took our precaution in advance,” and turn away, rejoicing"
  9,51,"Say, “Nothing will ever befall us except what God has destined for us. He is our Protector.” So in God let the believers put their trust"
  9,52,"Say, “Are you awaiting anything to befall us except one of the two best things: ˹victory or martyrdom˺? But We are awaiting God to afflict you with torment either from Him or at our hands. So keep waiting! We too are waiting with you.”"
  9,53,"Say, ˹O Prophet,˺ “˹Whether you˺ donate willingly or unwillingly, it will never be accepted from you, for you have been a rebellious people.”"
  9,54,"And what prevented their donations from being accepted is that they have lost faith in God and His Messenger, they never come to prayer except half-heartedly, and they never donate except resentfully"